author: Jorge Alonso
title: Watch A Cocky Tom Brady Murder Conan O’Brien In ‘For Honor’ On This Year’s Super Bowl Edition Of Clueless Gamer
text:
For the past three Super Bowls, Conan O’Brien has held a special edition of Clueless Gamer that features an NFL superstar playing video games with the late night host. 
This year, Tom Brady had the honor of killing Conan O’Brien and Dwight Freeney in Ubisoft’s upcoming action fighting game “For Honor”.
